Since the project emphasizes a premium and professional aesthetic, use the following prompts with an AI image generator (like Midjourney or DALL-E) to create consistent visual documentation.

### 7.1. Full System Architecture
> **Prompt:** A plain and professional system architecture diagram. Minimalist, clean flat design with simple icons: Mobile Phone, Server, Database, and a Brain for AI. No glows or neon, just a soft professional color palette of navy blue and white. High resolution, clear lines, professional technical diagram style.

### 7.2. Voice AI Workflow
> **Prompt:** A simple and professional flow diagram for Voice AI. Minimalist icons for microphone, processing, and output. Clean, flat design, no extra decorations. Professional corporate aesthetic, high clarity, white background. Clear arrows showing the data flow.

